Text: ...and it is in FLAC (that darned title was chopped off again).
This happens to be the best album ever made, IMO. Many thanks for the upload; let's see if I notice the difference.

You certainly will, with good enough headphones or speakers. Some people may perhaps find it somewhat "muddy" in comparison to the original or the Definitive (sic) Edition Remaster, but personally I prefer this one.

GREAT Download, THANKS FOR SHARING..
 Quality A+
